  "title": "Buyer | Jurong East | 5 Days | Up To $4.5K + PB - 4461",
  "description": "<p><strong>Procurement Officer / Buyer</strong><br />Basic Salary: $3,000 - $4,500  + Performance Bonus<br />Working Days: 5 Days per week<br />Office Location: Jurong East </p><p><strong>Key Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Manage the end-to-end procurement process, from sourcing suppliers [locally and overseas], to contract negotiation and final purchase orders</li><li>Develop and implement procurement strategies that drive cost-effectiveness and operational efficiency.</li><li>Conduct market research to identify potential suppliers and evaluate their suitability in terms of quality, price, and reliability.</li><li>Oversee company facilities, logistics and shipping arrangements (local & international)</li><li>Monitor, support and ensure compliance with company policies, legal regulations, ISO and HSE requirements.</li><li>Manage and maintain all licensing/insurance renewals for the company.</li><li>Handling of the company’s vehicles maintenance and licensing.</li><li>Resolve supplier disputes and address any issues related to delivery, quality, or performance.</li><li>Support cross-functional teams in project planning and procurement needs.</li><li>Monitor the inventory count and manage inventory records to anticipate future needs as well as ensure optimal inventory levels are maintained.</li><li>Carry out additional tasks as assigned by the section manager or supervisor.</li></ul><p><br /><strong>Email: supreme.jacksontan@gmail.com</strong></p><p><strong>Tan Yong Zhi (Jackson) | Reg: R24124461</strong></p><p><strong>The Supreme HR Advisory Pte. Ltd | EA No: 14C7279</strong></p>",
